Job Description:
A software development company is looking for a talented, long-term Senior NLP Engineer with strong skills in Python, experience in building ML services and launching models to production.

The company is a team of experts providing analytical services to healthcare clients. You will join an international team of first class professionals who are passionate to create products that improve quality of medical services.

We have the highest expectations in the industry regarding your ability to deliver high quality, performance, scalable, clean, and tested software.

Requirements:

Strong knowledge of Python;
Knowledge and experience with data-related Python packages (Pandas, NumPy, PyTorch, scikit-learn etc.);
Development of SQL queries for efficient data retrieval and manipulation;
Proficiency in NLP-related tasks, with a particular emphasis on Named Entity Recognition, Relation Extraction, and Knowledge Extraction;
Hands-on experience with embedding representations, the BERT model family, and transformer architectures;
Hands-on experience with Git;
Knowledge of Docker;
Experience with Hugging Face and Google Cloud would be a plus.

Benefits:

Flexible working hours;
Competitive salary;
Remote work;
Interesting projects to work on;
Paid vacations and sick leaves.

